data.description: This South County charmer is perfect for first-time buyers, savvy investors, small families or those looking to downsize. Upon entering this 1-2 bed home, you'll immediately notice the entire interior has been tastefully updated, reflecting a modern & inviting atmosphere. One of the standout features of this home is the addition of a mini-split in the rear bedroom. This high-efficiency heating & cooling system ensures comfort year-round while being energy-conscious. The remainder of the home benefits from a central HVAC system, providing optimal climate control throughout. Imagine starting your day with a cup of coffee in the cozy breakfast nook, or sharing a delightful meal w/ that special someone. The fenced rear yard will let the kids play freely or allow your pets to roam safely in this private outdoor space. It's a great extension of the home where you can enjoy outdoor activities and entertain friends and family. HERO PROGRAM MAY OFFER UP TO $30K, DEPENDING ON BUYER'S OCCUPATION.
